name: Snowball Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en: Snowball is a deflationary smart token that utilises the snowball effect in their marketing whilst rewarding holders passively.They are developing utility platforms on the BSC, including the Snowcial media app that pays users to browse a TikTok like social media interface. Snowball are also creating an all in one app interface that will feature an NFT market place, the Snowswap exchange, cash back rewards and a wallet for low market cap coins.
